	<div class="section spacer">
		<h2>About Spirit Ridge Vineyard Resort &amp; Spa</h2>

		<p><a href="http://www.spiritridge.ca" target="_blank">Spirit Ridge</a> is a beautiful resort located in Osoyoos, BC. Surrounded by the rolling vineyards of the South Okanagan wine country and overlooking Osoyoos Lake. Spirit Ridge offers a great wedding atmosphere. The resort is adjacent to the popular Nk'Mip Cellars Winery and features an on-site spa, golf course, pool, and a variety of restaurants.</p>

		<p>We chose Spirit Ridge because we wanted to have an all-outdoor, summer wedding in the Okanagan. What better place than Osoyoos, home of the warmest lake in Canada! The resort also features luxurious condo-style accommodations, making it the perfect summer getaway spot for our guests.</p>

