		<h2>Location</h2>
		<p>Osoyoos is located in the South Okanagan (about 1.5 hours south of Kelowna).</p>

		<p><b>From Vancouver area &mdash;</b>  Take Hwy. 1 East (The Trans-Canada) to Hope. Follow Hwy. 3 East to Osoyoos. Once in Osoyoos, Hwy 3 turns into Main Street. Continue on Main Street / Hwy 3, turn left on 45th Street and follow the signs to Spirit Ridge Vineyard Resort &amp; Spa.</p>

		<p><b>From Calgary area &mdash;</b>  Take Hwy. 1 West (The Trans-Canada) to Sicamous and follow Hwy. 97A South towards Vernon passing through Kelowna and Penticton and continue south on Hwy. 97 until you reach Osoyoos. Once in Osoyoos, drive east on Main Street / Hwy 3, turn left on 45th Street and follow the signs to Spirit Ridge Vineyard Resort &amp; Spa.</p>

		<p><b>From Kelowna area &mdash;</b> Drive south on Hwy. 97 and follow Hwy. 3 East to Osoyoos. At Osoyoos, turn left on Hwy. 3/Main Street. Continue on Main Street / Hwy 3, turn left on 45th Street and follow the signs to Spirit Ridge Vineyard Resort &amp; Spa.</p>

